snippet: Latanna Stone of Valrico, Fla., at 10 the youngest United States Women’s Amateur competitor, shot a 10-over-par 82 in the first round in Cleveland.
abstract: Ten-year-old Latanna Stone shoots a 10-over-par 82 in the first round of the United States Women’s Amateur.
lead_paragraph: Latanna Stone of Valrico, Fla., at 10 the youngest United States Women’s Amateur competitor, shot a 10-over-par 82 in the first round in Cleveland.
